{
  "number": 85,
  "name": "سُورَةُ البُرُوجِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Burooj",
  "englishNameTranslation": "The Constellations",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 5910,
      "text": "CONSIDER the sky full of great constellations,",
      "numberInSurah": 1,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5911,
      "text": "and [then bethink thyself of] the promised Day,",
      "numberInSurah": 2,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5912,
      "text": "and [of] Him who witnesses [all], and [of] that unto which witness is borne [by Him]!",
      "numberInSurah": 3,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5913,
      "text": "THEY DESTROY [but] themselves, they who would ready a pit",
      "numberInSurah": 4,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5914,
      "text": "of fire fiercely burning [for all who have attained to faith]!",
      "numberInSurah": 5,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5915,
      "text": "Lo! [With glee do] they contemplate that [fire],",
      "numberInSurah": 6,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5916,
      "text": "fully conscious of what they are doing to the believers,",
      "numberInSurah": 7,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5917,
      "text": "whom they hate for no other reason than that they believe in God, the Almighty, the One to whom all praise is due,",
      "numberInSurah": 8,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5918,
      "text": "[and] to whom the dominion of the heavens and the earth belongs. But God is witness unto everything!",
      "numberInSurah": 9,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5919,
      "text": "Verily, as for those who persecute believing men and believing women, and thereafter do not repent, hell's suffering awaits them: yea, suffering through fire awaits them!",
      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5920,
      "text": "[But,] verily, they who attain to faith and do righteous deeds shall [in the life to come] have gardens through which running waters flow - that triumph most great!",
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5921,
      "text": "VERILY, thy Sustainer's grip is exceedingly strong!",
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5922,
      "text": "Behold, it is He who creates [man] in the first instance, and He [it is who] will bring him forth anew.",
      "numberInSurah": 13,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5923,
      "text": "And He alone is truly-forgiving, all-embracing in His love,",
      "numberInSurah": 14,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5924,
      "text": "in sublime almightiness enthroned,",
      "numberInSurah": 15,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5925,
      "text": "a sovereign doer of whatever He wills.",
      "numberInSurah": 16,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5926,
      "text": "HAS IT ever come within thy ken, the story of the [sinful] hosts",
      "numberInSurah": 17,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5927,
      "text": "of Pharaoh, and of [the tribe of] Thamud?",
      "numberInSurah": 18,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5928,
      "text": "And yet, they who are bent on denying the truth persist in giving it the lie:",
      "numberInSurah": 19,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5929,
      "text": "but all the while God encompasses them [with His knowledge and might] without their being aware of it.",
      "numberInSurah": 20,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 590,
      "ruku": 527,
      "hizbQuarter": 236,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
